products.name: The Godfather
products.description: The Godfather is a crime novel by American author Mario Puzo. Originally published on 10 March 1969 by G. P. Putnam's Sons, the novel details the story of a fictional Mafia family in New York City and Long Island, headed by Vito Corleone, the Godfather.

products.name: Dilwale
products.description: Raj and Meera fall in love, but are forced to stay away from each other as they belong to rival mafia families. Years later, they get a second chance when their siblings fall for each other.

products.name: Avatar
products.description: Jake, a paraplegic marine, replaces his brother on the Na'vi-inhabited Pandora for a corporate mission. He is accepted by the natives as one of their own, but he must decide where his loyalties lie.

products.name: The Dark Knight
products.description: Batman has a new foe, the Joker, who is an accomplished criminal hell-bent on decimating Gotham City. Together with Gordon and Harvey Dent, Batman struggles to thwart the Joker before it is too late.

products.name: Dhoom 3
products.description: Dhoom 3 is an action-packed Bollywood film directed by Vijay Krishna Acharya. The movie follows Sahir, a skilled circus performer and a master thief, who seeks revenge against a corrupt bank in Chicago that wronged his father. As Sahir orchestrates a series of heists, two cops, Jai and Ali, are called in to stop him. The film is known for its high-octane action sequences, daring stunts, and thrilling cat-and-mouse chase scenes. It also explores themes of revenge, family, and justice, while showcasing a strong emotional core between Sahir and his mute twin brother Samar.

products.name: Golmaal Again
products.description: Five orphan men return to the orphanage they grew up in to attend their mentor's funeral. However, they encounter the ghost of their childhood friend, Khushi, and help her attain salvation.

products.name: The Lord of the Rings
products.description: The Lord of the Rings: The Fellowship of the Ring is a high-fantasy epic directed by Peter Jackson, based on J.R.R. Tolkien's novel of the same name. The story begins in the peaceful land of the Shire, where a young hobbit named Frodo Baggins inherits a powerful ring that could bring about the destruction of Middle-earth if it falls into the hands of the dark lord Sauron. To prevent this, Frodo sets out on a perilous journey, accompanied by a diverse group of allies known as the Fellowship of the Ring, including Aragorn, Legolas, Gimli, Boromir, and Frodo's loyal friend Sam. Together, they face various challenges and adversaries as they seek to destroy the ring in the fires of Mount Doom. The film is praised for its stunning visuals, compelling storytelling, and rich character development, marking the beginning of an iconic cinematic trilogy.

products.name: Tiger Zinda Hai
products.description: Tiger Zinda Hai is an Indian action thriller film directed by Ali Abbas Zafar and is a sequel to the 2012 film Ek Tha Tiger. The story follows Indian spy Tiger (played by Salman Khan) and his wife Zoya (played by Katrina Kaif), who are tasked with rescuing a group of Indian nurses held captive by a terrorist organization in Iraq. As they embark on a dangerous mission, they must use their skills, teamwork, and determination to save the hostages while facing numerous obstacles and threats. The film is known for its high-energy action sequences, emotional depth, and strong performances, particularly from its lead actors.

products.name: Pathaan
products.description: Pathaan is an action thriller film directed by Siddharth Anand, featuring Shah Rukh Khan in the titular role as Pathaan, a skilled secret agent. The story revolves around Pathaan's mission to thwart a terrorist plot led by the menacing antagonist, played by John Abraham. The film showcases high-octane action sequences, espionage, and elaborate stunts as Pathaan teams up with a fierce intelligence operative, played by Deepika Padukone. As they delve into a world of betrayal and danger, they must navigate challenges that test their skills and resolve. Pathaan is notable for its engaging plot, stunning visuals, and Shah Rukh Khan's return to action cinema.

products.name: Avengers: Endgame
products.description: Avengers: Endgame is the epic conclusion to the Marvel Cinematic Universe's Infinity Saga, directed by Anthony and Joe Russo. The film picks up after the devastating events of Avengers: Infinity War, where the villain Thanos used the Infinity Stones to erase half of all life in the universe. The remaining Avengers and their allies, including Iron Man, Captain America, Thor, and Black Widow, must come together to devise a plan to undo Thanos' actions. The film explores themes of sacrifice, friendship, and heroism, culminating in an epic showdown against Thanos. It features time travel, emotional farewells, and significant character arcs, making it a landmark film in superhero cinema.

products.name: Spider-Man
products.description: Spider-Man: No Way Home is a superhero film from the Marvel Cinematic Universe (MCU), directed by Jon Watts. It follows Peter Parker (Spider-Man), played by Tom Holland, as he deals with the fallout from his secret identity being exposed to the world by Mysterio in the previous film. Desperate to fix his life, Peter seeks help from Doctor Strange, but their attempt to alter reality goes wrong, opening up the multiverse and bringing villains from other dimensions, including Green Goblin, Doctor Octopus, and Electro, into Peter's world. The film is known for its fan-service moments, action sequences, and the return of previous Spider-Men, Tobey Maguire and Andrew Garfield, making it a celebration of the Spider-Man legacy.

products.name: Thugs of Hindostan
products.description: Thugs of Hindostan is a Bollywood period action-adventure film set in 1795, during British colonial rule in India. The story follows a group of Indian rebels, or thugs,led by the fierce warrior Khudabaksh Azaad, who are fighting to free their land from British oppression. The British East India Company sends a small-time conman, Firangi Mallah, to infiltrate and betray the rebels. However, Firangiâ€™s allegiances constantly shift as he navigates a world of betrayal, loyalty, and resistance. The film is known for its grand visuals, elaborate set pieces, and epic battle sequences, but also faced mixed reviews due to its narrative.

products.name: The Revenant
products.description: A frontiersman on a quest for survival seeks vengeance against those who left him for dead.

products.name: Superbad
products.description: Two high school friends navigate a chaotic night of parties and misadventures before graduation.

products.name: Get Out
products.description: A young African American man uncovers shocking secrets when he meets his white girlfriend's family.

products.name: Zootopia
products.description: In a city of anthropomorphic animals, a rabbit police officer and a cynical con artist fox must work together.

products.name: Tenet
products.description: A secret agent embarks on a time-bending mission to prevent World War III.

products.name: A Star is Born
products.description: A seasoned musician helps a young singer find fame while battling his own personal demons.

products.name: The Hobbit: An Unexpected Journey
products.description: A hobbit embarks on an epic quest to help a group of dwarves reclaim their homeland from a dragon.

products.name: Interstellar
products.description: A team of explorers travels through a wormhole in space in search of a new home for humanity.
